{"tid":1425680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打：和理非 宜家接受程度愈黎愈高","createTime":"2019-08-06T19:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:49:53.000Z","uid":268538,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8b90633d758431b9f3b2b24d21fc3a9e4df7d9","tid":1425680,"uid":268538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:31:43.000Z","msg":"成個運動開始佐成2個月<br />\n次次搞遊行10次有8次都會去<br />\n見證住100萬人上街.<br />\n612事件. 之後演變成200人上街<br />\n政府咩都唔回應 演變成宜家局面<br />\n由原本反對拋磚頭 覺得好暴力<br />\n宜家已經發展到好想拆佐成間狗屋佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老爸係退休警察淺藍 之前同佢講發夢嘅事<br />\n佢會幫住警察 話味必個個係咁 重覺得我地係搞事分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢無阻止過我出去 但次次俾親啲黑警video 佢睇<br />\n佢都黑曬面 又嘈大交咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直至經歷完元朗白衫打人事件 老豆由淺藍變佐黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日係到屌鳩啲警察 話警黑合作得咁明顯 屌曬鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始無法無天。<br />\n老媽係淺黃變佐深黃 成日睇直播都好擔心啲勇武派被拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢見到警察被踢落扶手電梯個段video 話打得好！<br />\n平時啲仆街打得啲年青人咁兇狠阿拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重讚你地好有精力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老媽好想同大家講<br />\n如果自己友太小人就走，唔好戀戰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想再見到年青人被拉，當然人多就可以留。<br />\n打人係大快人心，叫佢地自己食返<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但千其唔好打死人。</span></strong><br />\n宜家局勢就係睇緊邊面有第一個犧牲者。<br />\n因為會好影響民意。<br />\n同埋老媽其實唔係好buy 不合作運動. <br />\n會覺得影響到其他人. 雖然佢唔介意. <br />\n但佢都唔想大家失去民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老爸就會話 <br />\n其實人地全副裝備有曬武器邊夠打阿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收工除佐裝備味又係普通人一個 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時俾人打唔好怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我<br />\n希望大家不被捕 一齊黎一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家叫現場人士唔好影相有禮貌啲<br />\n<br />\n我地成家支持大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938a6a87b73e52748c94c4740f2b5b9307925cc4","tid":1425680,"uid":268538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:38:04.000Z","msg":"推一推。"},{"pid":"9629c6c828320f1bad2cedfc723cccdb1f909791","tid":1425680,"uid":119283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:40:55.000Z","msg":"正確思路。<br />\n核彈都唔割。<br />\n兄弟姊妹一世 。"},{"pid":"8a8a7ab080eeb8902a158f8b09fc5dcd5ca5d6ae","tid":1425680,"uid":60749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:42:49.000Z","msg":"收工除咗裝備咪又係普通人一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a62079be7cfa46d76575ec92f37c455a5200d3a","tid":1425680,"uid":80139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"羨慕絲打有明事理嘅父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2135dc2ddd59a2701f99d1341c11080f5dfac8","tid":1425680,"uid":268538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:44:54.000Z","msg":"由於我真係無咩用<br />\n跑又跑唔郁 衝前又唔得<br />\n最多只係傳過物資<br />\n夾份買佐豬嘴同頭盔同濾罐俾大家<br />\n希望大家一齊努力 各自爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c170995d884a7eab52a672878e02e7441d82fa7","tid":1425680,"uid":37350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:45:01.000Z","msg":"不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不分化、不指責、不割席、不篤灰"},{"pid":"9481393500f9e2db060d32bde707cc8c944729c3","tid":1425680,"uid":289620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:45:01.000Z","msg":"和理非唔割前線嘅同時<br />\n前線都唔好割和理非"},{"pid":"76684bb45ff302d6ba3357ec417164a5e8c56ec9","tid":1425680,"uid":22155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:46:01.000Z","m